Package: rankedBeliefR
Type: Package
Title: R Bindings for the ranked_belief Library
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person(given = "Ranked", family = "Belief", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "ranked-belief@example.com")
Description: Provides an R interface to the ranked_belief lazy ranking library.
    The package wraps the stable C interoperability layer so that ranked
    belief sequences can be created, combined, and observed from R while
    preserving the library's lazy semantics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: C++20, CMake-built ranked_belief_c_api in ../../build
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
NeedsCompilation: yes
